1
00:00:05,340 --> 00:00:09,140
Infinite in mystery is the gift of the

2
00:00:09,140 --> 00:00:09,640
goddess.

3
00:00:10,740 --> 00:00:14,000
We seek it thus and take to the

4
00:00:14,000 --> 00:00:14,520
sky.

5
00:00:16,260 --> 00:00:19,160
Ripples form on the water's surface.

6
00:00:19,900 --> 00:00:22,660
The wandering soul knows no rest.

7
00:00:25,720 --> 00:00:27,880
Loveless, act one.

8
00:00:29,760 --> 00:00:31,439
Hmph, you remembered.

9
00:00:36,500 --> 00:00:39,060
How can I not, when you've beaten it

10
00:00:39,060 --> 00:00:39,800
into my head?

11
00:00:44,640 --> 00:00:46,400
Don't take Sephiroth lightly.

12
00:00:47,600 --> 00:00:50,020
Hmph, noted.

13
00:01:18,520 --> 00:01:21,280
Huh, is that the best you can do?

14
00:01:25,720 --> 00:01:27,660
All hail Sephiroth, huh?

15
00:01:28,820 --> 00:01:31,240
Angeal, stay back.

16
00:01:32,140 --> 00:01:34,200
I'll take Sephiroth alone.

17
00:01:34,840 --> 00:01:35,320
Genesis!

18
00:01:37,220 --> 00:01:39,420
The world needs a new hero.

19
00:01:42,480 --> 00:01:44,500
Come and try.

20
00:01:44,780 --> 00:01:47,540
So smug, but for how long?

21
00:02:36,840 --> 00:02:37,440
Stop!

22
00:02:38,160 --> 00:02:39,780
You'll destroy this place.

23
00:02:40,500 --> 00:02:43,000
That's no way to talk to a hero.

24
00:03:38,800 --> 00:03:40,560
Enough!

25
00:03:43,320 --> 00:03:44,400
Angeal.

26
00:03:45,480 --> 00:03:46,980
Out of my way!

27
00:03:54,000 --> 00:03:55,080
Genesis!

